{"tid":117473,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"愛腳之仕小心！1司機因瀨腳坐監！","createTime":"2017-02-12T09:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T16:11:05.000Z","uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63de426664a0ba5910479de35059efb4677e4945","tid":117473,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T09:09:48.000Z","msg":"愛腳之仕小心！1司機因瀨腳坐監！<br />\n<br />\n根據日本媒體報導，日本一位56歲的男性老司機於去年7月至9月間，在京都市伏見區的停車場內，以幫女生修理汽車為由怒瀨坐在駕駛座上的女生腳20至35分鐘。 <br />\n<br />\n該老司機於去年12月被警方逮捕，今年2月10日京都地裁法院認為這位老司機的行為雖然猥褻性並不高，但給被害者帶來了不快造成了傷害，法院以強制猥褻罪判處該男子2年有期徒刑，緩刑4年執行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.gameapps.hk/images/201702/11/DSSS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F201702%2F11%2FDSSS4.jpg&h=99fca224&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d867f1d7fc6ef6fbbf44e5a74a049f470074d1a","tid":117473,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"腦魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087aae66079b839242c8b9040f0fb1d135049c6c","tid":117473,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T09:21:23.000Z","msg":"出錯波台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb764dfe269c5fa0a13da7a36beccb6d7a06595b","tid":117473,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T09:25:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3107fc32a4f68c789b40b2b87c767e8d46847a","tid":117473,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T09:26:34.000Z","msg":"可以賴足半個鐘? 時間停止?"},{"pid":"3937201d58bcc7b0663b5f1cf9b7661afc4c1b2b","tid":117473,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T09:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8753c4a0694cda25bb7cbc85ecbe1d36b226df","tid":117473,"uid":53223,"like":0,"di